name: Mezzo Canyon
description:
Introduction

Approach

Set off on the Cathedral Rock trailhead. When the trail splits, go to the left (e.g. Little Falls approach). When the trail ends, cross-country traverse to Mezzo canyon.

Descent

Exit

After the last drop, look for a use trail down canyon left. Follow this to the Mary Jane trailhead.

Red tape

If early in the season be sure to call the ranger station to see if the trailhead is open. If there is snow it is likely to be closed.
